<h1>Privacy Policy for Images2PDF</h1>
<p><br/>Images2PDF values your privacy. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our mobile application Images2PDF ("the App"). By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>
<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect the following types of information when you use the App:<br/><br/></p>
<p><strong>a. Personal Information</strong><br/>We do not collect any personal information such as your name, email, or contact details unless you explicitly provide it.</p>
<p><strong>b. Camera Access</strong><br/>The App requires access to your device&rsquo;s camera in order to allow you to take photos that can be converted to PDF documents. We do not collect or store any images or video from your camera. All images captured are used solely for the purpose of creating PDF files within the App.</p>
<p><strong>c. Photo Library Access</strong><br/>The App may request access to your device's photo library to allow you to select images to convert to PDF. We do not collect or store these images; they are processed locally on your device.</p>
<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p><br/>We use the information collected to:</p>
<p>Allow you to capture and upload images for PDF creation locally on your device. we do not send any informtion on our server.</p>
<h2><br/>3. Sharing of Information</h2>
<p><br/>We do not share your personal information, images, or any other data collected from your use of the App with third parties, except as required by law.</p>
<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<p><br/>We take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure.</p>
<h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p><br/>The App may include links to third-party websites or services, such as cloud storage or social media platforms, for sharing your PDF files. These third-party services may collect data in accordance with their own privacy policies. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of these services before using them.</p>
<h2></h2>
<h2></h2>
<h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p><br/>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted to this page with an updated effective date. We encourage you to review this privacy policy periodically for any updates.</p>
